Description| **Vertical component of motion anchored to the reference geodetic model. Ortho products are resampled to a 100 m grid. The EGMS Ortho product exploits the information provided by ascending and descending orbits of the EGMS Calibrated product to derive the layer of purely vertical displacements. EGMS Ortho Vertical is visualised as a vector map of measurement points colour-coded by average velocity (vertical components) and distributed to users in comma-separated values format. Each point is associated with a time series of displacement, i.e. a plot with values of displacement per acquisition of the satellite.** 
Satellite| **Copernicus Sentinel-2 MSI L1C** 
Orbit Direction| **DESCENDING** 
Measurement Period| **2018-01-01 / 2022-12-31** 
Provider| **European Environment Agency (EEA)**
